cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.CC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the height of languages, which is a fundamental concept in formal language theory. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper applies the results to logical complexity. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper develops new techniques for bounding the height of languages. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper deals with complexity measures of languages. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper applies the results to the complexity of logical languages.
